weren't putting me on...

25:22.210 --> 25:26.630
that you were Emerson Thorne,
ambitious young law student...

25:26.790 --> 25:28.950
and all that crap.

25:29.670 --> 25:32.800
What about that kiss and all that crap?

25:33.380 --> 25:36.960
There's more where that came from,
Emerson Thorne.

25:37.300 --> 25:41.300
