43:28.250 --> 43:33.130
- I hope I'm not interrupting anything.
- Come in, Kelly. Porter's all steamed up.

43:33.300 --> 43:36.090
- Too much partying.
- You listen to me, hippie.

43:36.300 --> 43:38.680
